#!/usr/bin/env ruby
irb -r numru/gdir_connect_ftp-like

=begin
= NAME

gdir_client - A client of gdir_server using irb.

= SYNOPSIS

  % gdir_client top_dir [[host:]port] [-a allowed_address] ...

= DESCRIPTION

((*gdir_client*)) command is just equal to

   irb -r numru/gdir_connect_ftp-like

= OPTIONS

same as gdir_server

= SEE ALSO

((*gdir_server(1)*))

=end
